snippet.title: Ninja Turtles: Mutant Rumble - Part 1 / Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles gameplay 2017
snippet.description:
Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Mutant Rumble gameplay - help Ninja Turtles to clear city streets from villains.
NEXT➤https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UGV1kVI6Rsc&index=2&list=PLyEWMoAQV3jm0yl8UAqVAuYaRKxhK0KXQ PLAYLIST➤https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLyEWMoAQV3jm0yl8UAqVAuYaRKxhK0KXQ 🔝Subscribe➤  https://www.youtube.com/c/angryfungames?sub_confirmation=1
Thanks for every  💕Like  ⤴Share  ✏️ Comment and 🌟Add in Playlists. Your support is greatly appreciated ↘ ↘ ↘

The plot develops in the same familiar to the turtles of New York, where the roofs, streets and sewers attacking powerful enemies, including Baxter, Fishfeys, Dogpaund, Schroeder and others. But not for nothing that you have been studying karate and have become experts in these martial arts, just you and be able to resist them, beating off attack after attack. Save the peaceful existence of the rest of the city and its citizens. 

In addition to karate you can get help and some auxiliary equipment such as smoke grenades, thunder and lightning, they are great help to disperse large clumps of enemies can stun or distract them. Just do not forget about his friend April, which always helps speed up the process of curing wounds and possibly save your life! 

On my youtube channel you can watch else:
